cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper is about using advanced LSTM for emotion recognition, which is a task related to natural language processing and speech processing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper uses weighted pooling RNN, which is a technique commonly used in computer vision, suggesting that it could also belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper also involves artificial intelligence techniques, which suggests that it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper involves neural networks, which suggests that it could belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
